'''Brother Jered''' is a [[monk]] at the [[Edgeville Monastery]]. Players may speak to him to have their [[holy symbol]]s blessed one at a time. Since he is on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}}, only those with a [[Prayer]] level of 31 can access him. Players who achieve [[Skill mastery|level 99]] Prayer may purchase the [[Prayer cape]] from him for 99,000 [[coins]].

Brother Jered is unable to assist the player in the [[2021 Halloween event]] on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}}, exclaiming to come see him downstairs for his paperwork (where [[Brother Jered (2021 Halloween event)|his 2021 Halloween event NPC]] is also located).

==Stock==
Note: If a player has multiple [[Skill mastery|99s]], they will receive the trimmed variant of the cape instead.
